Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅大人為何想從我們的保護之下逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身處的時間和空間都跟我們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能瞭解她的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當她的保姆實在是當膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此 對我們來說 她是必不可缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 屬下定會將她帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒什麼時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白娜絲 我進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆帶回來那個女孩子的病歷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療的時候有點在意 就去查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:00:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可不是一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(714,500)\pos(175,380)\fnSimSun\fs30}第三話 「千年的迷惑」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將這裡稱為掩體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩體？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口藏在群山之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有潛沙才能進來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古人好像是將這裡建成安全的避難場所了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆帶回來的那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療的時候我查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構成Theseus的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是經過完美設計的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為Ideal Children的克隆人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她的身體特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更接近我們拿度亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的事情 之前也碰到過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醫治的那個Theseus傷兵 他的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拿度亞的克隆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想到的結論只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應該是經過完美設計的IC克隆體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為反復的複製而劣化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能利用了我們拿度亞的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定那個女孩也...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩 可不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡遺留著當時的機械
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的“古魚”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}古魚：第一集男主開的那臺浮游沙上摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有能潛沙的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是在這裡找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能啟動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我有進行維護 隨時都能開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我沒騙你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我能不能開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等你好了 我教你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 想讓你看的東西在其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 嚇了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可以說是進行量子躍遷和逆操作的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將它——莫諾克洛斯打入到擬似相變立場去 就可以中和立場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然太深奧了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能把那沙鯨——OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關在沙裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們在追捕著OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 量子躍遷引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我哥哥讓它們重新綻放光芒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在追捕OZMA的時候 他失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成它...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是個了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我長得多麼高 也比不上他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能用它打倒OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就能看到哥哥的背影了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆 你回船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想問瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅 你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞你相當於是Theseus的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼要一個人駕駛著帆船逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theseus軍在找我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們很快就會找到這裡來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓你們再次陷入危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我也不知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了見你們稱之為沙鯨的OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見OZMA？ 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我想回答 也沒有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那千年的悠久時光中 我一直迷惑著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺一直在尋找著那份答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅累了 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是要治好身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回船上去吧 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這種地方幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 她的情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在醫生在診斷中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能那麼簡單就有結果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明看起來才十幾二十歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端粒居然這麼短
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}端粒：染色體末端的DNA重複序列
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天額外加菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家盡情吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要大吃一頓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從地獄轉了一圈回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上天堂之前 吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞開吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 昨天真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 差點就被蒸熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theseus那些傢夥 為什麼盯上我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是因為精力旺盛的小朋友帶回來的那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人 給巴魯丹諾斯帶來了厄運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 索留 你剛才說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在談論了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你帶回來的是可怕的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 精力旺盛的小朋友就這點能耐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們有必要去幫他一把
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是久違的美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我參戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩 我們也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說我在吃飯中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起雞皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅 你看到那個女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛轉個身 她就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢夥 給我安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆 瑪雅溜出醫務室 不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我在船內找了一遍 但沒看到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我能不能開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等你好了 我教你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅對沙上摩托感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那種沙摩...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到掩體去的話 可以找到幾臺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打算穿過環礁 逃到沙漠中去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶她回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼想要逃離我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是正確的 什麼是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼對議案進行表決
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多數贊成 議案通過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是為了我們能繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為這顆星球的盟主進行長久的統治
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真魁梧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基多大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言下之意 您是看中這個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們IC 擁有最完美的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而存在於世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學的缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就在於它能讓人類喪失尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"心臟"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到那裡的話 未來應該就會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你見面 說不定能明白一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回船上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅身體 想穿過沙海簡直就是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無需逃避 巴魯丹諾斯會接受你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯丹諾斯是所有人的家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不想讓大家再次陷入危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是OZMA嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 要"保護"拿度亞少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那少年是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不允許有人加害於他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把瑪雅還給我 假面混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我跟你沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把瑪雅大人帶回艦內
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 基多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 拜託 幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦前方2000 出現巨大的擬似相變立場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙賊的潛沙艦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 範圍太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急潛航
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆 薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快將瑪雅大人帶回艦內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎比他哥哥還要賊運亨通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆打算獨自去救瑪雅回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 有Theseus的最新型潛沙艦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 這樣一來就是沙中的全面對決了
